text: Oh wow thats so cool thanks for sharing that with me! Yeah i find being in a large group of people very overwhelming:laughing:. That is very true, i agree :+1::skin-tone-3:

And yes i have written a few things in my personal statment, actually more like noted down. I’m now trying to structure it well so that it is intresting to read. I’m not sure why i am so anxious in writing this personal statement, i think its the pressure and also the expectations that are set.

I was on unifrog the other day and it suggested me a lot of universities that i can go to for psychology. Now i’m not sure if i should move out or stay home, because a lot of unis that were suggested were far away from me. I know theres a lot of pros and cons to moving out what do you think?:thinking_face:
